configuration.name: forceConfig.soqlQuery
configuration.value:
select
Id,
Is_GTM_Partner__c,
Is_Rebate_Partner__c,
ISCUSTOMERPORTAL,
ISPARTNER,
LASTMODIFIEDBYID,
LASTMODIFIEDDATE,
NAME,
NAMELOCAL,
NEW_OWNER__C,
NON_ELIGIBLE_LOBS__C,
NUMBEROFEMPLOYEES,
OWNERID,
PARENTID,
PHONE,
PHONE_ACTION__C,
RAD_CODE__C,
Rating,
RECORDTYPEID
FROM
account  WHERE LASTMODIFIEDDATE  > ${OFFSET}  
ORDER BY LASTMODIFIEDDATE
